## Task Router

| User Need | Task File | When |
|---|---|---|
| Audit a landing page | `tasks/landing-page-audit.md` | Single page with traffic but low conversion |
| Analyse a funnel | `tasks/funnel-analysis.md` | Multi-step drop-off diagnosis |
| Design an A/B test | `tasks/ab-test-design.md` | Planning a specific experiment |
| Interpret heatmaps | `tasks/heatmap-interpretation.md` | Have Hotjar/Clarity/FullStory data to turn into insights |
| Build a CRO roadmap | `tasks/cro-roadmap.md` | Prioritising a backlog of test ideas over a quarter |

**Routing rules:**
1. Single page in scope → `landing-page-audit.md`.
2. Multi-step journey → `funnel-analysis.md`, then `ab-test-design.md` for the biggest leak.
3. Existing recordings/heatmaps to interpret → `heatmap-interpretation.md` first, then A/B design.
4. Quarterly planning / backlog grooming → `cro-roadmap.md`.

**Load task:** Read the task file, then execute its workflow.

